  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Social Dialogue Facility 2015. LO/FTF and DI. Colombia.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the project is to contribute to the overall goal of the Danish development assistance
to civil society, which is to: contribute to inclusive growth and decent jobs in developing
countries. The strategic objective of this project is to promote consensus in Colombia about bi- and tripartite social dialogue as key to developing a well-functioning labour market, which is a cornerstone for building a sustainable society. The
project will support and capacitate employers and employees with tools and knowledge on how
to perform and facilitate social dialogue, which will enable them to develop a more stable
working environment at enterprise level.</narrative>
  </description>
